OL,4,Cdiscovered at motorway services
OL,6,FA "significant" cockroach infestation
OL,7,Fhas been discovered at a motorway
OL,8,Fservice station in Oxfordshire.
OL,10,FEnvironmental health officers from
OL,11,FSouth Oxfordshire District Council
OL,12,Fcarried out an emergency investigation
OL,13,Fat Welcome Break off the M40 near
OL,14,FOxford after a member of the public
OL,15,Fcomplained.
OL,17,FFour units in the main building were
OL,18,Fforced to close immediately, including
OL,19,FKFC, The Good Breakfast, Chopstix and
OL,20,FStarbucks.
