OL,6,FEvidence of a cockroach infestation
OL,7,Fwas found in the food preparation and
OL,8,Fservery areas of the outlets which
OL,9,Fposed a "significant risk of food
OL,10,Fcontamination and an imminent risk to
OL,11,Fthe customers' health".
OL,13,FThe businesses at the site, off
OL,14,FJunction 8 near Wheatley, will remain
OL,15,Fclosed until officers deem the health
OL,16,Frisk has been removed.
