OL,6,FOn Friday 31 May, during a hearing at
OL,7,FOxford Magistrates' Court, District
OL,8,FJudge Rana reviewed the evidence and
OL,9,Fstatements provided by the officers
OL,10,Fand confirmed the imminent health risk
OL,11,Fon 20 May and was satisfied that the
OL,12,Frisk to health remained in place.
OL,14,FThe judge made a Hygiene Emergency
OL,15,FProhibition Order and also awarded
OL,16,Ffull costs of just over #3,000 to
OL,17,FSouth Oxfordshire District Council.
