OL,6,FPaul Fielding, Head of Housing and
OL,7,FEnvironment at South Oxfordshire
OL,8,FDistrict Council, said: "When we
OL,9,Freceived the initial complaint, our
OL,10,FEnvironmental Health officers took
OL,11,Fimmediate action and carried out an
OL,12,Finvestigation at Welcome Break
OL,13,FServices and served the hygiene
OL,14,Femergency prohibition notice requiring
OL,15,Fthe temporary closure of the affected
OL,16,Fbusinesses.
