OL,6,F"The infestation presented a
OL,7,Fsignification risk of contamination
OL,8,Fand a serious risk to public health
OL,9,Fand I'm pleased that the District
OL,10,FJudge has now endorsed the action our
OL,11,Fofficers took.
OL,13,F"Our officers will continue conducting
OL,14,Fregular inspections at the site in
OL,15,Forder to protect public health.
OL,17,F"They are also working with Welcome
OL,18,FBreak to address the issue and
OL,19,Fsupporting their efforts to reopen the
OL,20,Fimpacted units as soon as possible."
